res = client.get('/users', query_string={'skip': 'string', 'limit':
    'string'}, headers={'Content-Type': 'application/json'})
assert res.status_code == 422
res = client.get('/users', query_string={'skip': -1}, headers={
    'Content-Type': 'application/json'})
assert res.status_code == 422
res = client.get('/users', query_string={'limit': -1}, headers={
    'Content-Type': 'application/json'})
assert res.status_code == 422
res = client.get('/users', query_string={'limit': 101}, headers={
    'Content-Type': 'application/json'})
assert res.status_code == 422
